  "text": "which means that the BIBO stability of the closed-loop system is guaranteed under switching. Here inequality (a) follows from the triangle inequality of the norm, (b) is based on the facts that the norm of a composition operator is upper bounded by the multiplicative product of individual operator's norms and that the H ∞ norm of a linear operator equals the induced norm of input-output power (RMS value) [CITATION_1] , and (c) is shown in (5).",
